snippet.title: WAR 2 | Official Trailer | Hrithik Roshan | NTR | Kiara Advani | Ayan Mukerji | YRF Spy Universe
snippet.description:
Get ready for the storm, the WAR begins now! #War2Trailer is out!
#War2 releasing in Hindi, Telugu & Tamil on August 14th in cinemas worldwide! #YRFSpyUniverse

‚ñ∫ Subscribe Now: https://goo.gl/xs3mrY üîî Stay updated!

üé¨ MOVIE CREDITS:
Movie: WAR 2
Starring: Hrithik Roshan, NTR, Kiara Advani
Director: Ayan Mukerji
Producer: Aditya Chopra
Co-Producer: Akshaye Widhani
Screenplay: Shridhar Raghavan
Director of Photography: Benjamin Jasper ACS 
Music: Pritam
Lyrics: Amitabh Bhattacharya
Dialogues: Abbas Tyrewala
Story: Aditya Chopra
Associate Producer: Rishabh Chopra
Executive Producer: Sanjay Shivalkar
Editor: Aarif Sheikh
Production Designers: Rajat Poddar, Amrita Mahal Nakai
Sound: Dileep Subramaniam, Ganesh Gangadharan
Background Music: Sanchit Balhara, Ankit Balhara
Action Directors: Spiro Razatos, Franz Spilhaus, Anl Arasu, Oh Sea Young, Craig Macrae, Sunil Rodrigues [ROD]
Costume Designers: Anaita Shroff Adajania, Niharika Jolly
Director of Choreography: Bosco Leslie Martis
Visual Effects Studio: yFX
Casting Director: Shanoo Sharma
Supervising Producer: Gurpreet Singh
Trailers & Promos: Mohit Sajnaney
Release Date: 14 August 2025

The film will be available with audio descriptions and closed captioning.

About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger", starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2" is the sixth film of the YRF Spy Universe franchise and will release on 14 August 2025. The film stars two of the greatest cinematic icons Hrithik Roshan and NTR, with Kiara Advani in the lead and is directed by Ayan Mukerji. ‚ÄúAlpha‚Äù, the seventh instalment in the franchise and Hindi cinema's first female-led YRF Spy Universe film, starring Alia Bhatt and Sharvari, is set to release on 25 December 2025.

Synopsis:
Yash Raj Films‚Äô Saiyaara is an intense love story, that launches Ahaan Panday and Aneet Padda as the next YRF hero and heroine respectively. 

Directed by Mohit Suri, a master of the romance genre, Saiyaara tells a pure-hearted love story of two youngsters Vaani and Krish. While Vaani writes, Krish sings and they both make music together. Though poles apart in their lives, beliefs and backgrounds, Vaani and Krish are perfect with each other and for each other. Will they understand that truth despite their age, their problems? 

They say flawed, imperfect people make for a perfect love story‚Ä¶and Saiyaara is about celebrating that one love story that is so deep, so pure and so caring that it is absolutely unconditional.

Vaani and Krish will have to navigate life, their problems, their insecurities to hopefully realise that only love can be the answer to everything. Saiyaara is a film that celebrates every season of love through the eyes of Vaani & Krish and poses a simple question‚Ä¶do you love someone so much that you would bet everything to keep that person in your life?

snippet.title: WE OUTSIDE | YELHOMIE | OFFICIAL MUSIC VIDEO | @massappealindia
snippet.description:
We Outside by Yelhomie with Augustine Shimray and Sajou Chenglei.

Stream We Outside: https://orcd.co/weoutside_yelhomie

Label: Mass Appeal

Song description:
‚ÄúWe Outside‚Äù is not just a track it‚Äôs a defiant anthem born from pain, protest, and resistance. Written amidst curfews, gunshots, and internet blackouts in war-torn Manipur, Yelhomie confronts state violence, systemic oppression, and the harsh realities faced by his Indigenous community during the 2023 conflict.
Opening with a haunting tribal chant ‚ÄúCarry the shield, hold the spear‚Äù sung by Augustine from Featherheads (Ukhrul, Manipur), the song sets the tone for a battle cry steeped in ancestral strength. Produced by Seej from Mizoram, the beat fuses Indigenous tribal textures with raw hip-hop grit, giving voice to a region often left in 
silence.

With hard-hitting bars like ‚ÄúHeavier the pants, the dreams don‚Äôt fly‚Äù, Yelhomie captures the tragic transformation of students and dreamers into reluctant warriors. The youth, once full of ambition, now carry arms not by choice, but by necessity, victims of a system that fuels chaos to suppress dissent.

The outro features a spiritual invocation in Ancient Meitei-lon written in Meitei Mayek script ‚Äî a wake-up call to the Yel-hou-mee, the Indigenous people of Manipur, delivered by Oja Sajoubi Chenglei of the Puya temple board (Puya refers to the holy book of Sanamahism, religion of the indigenous Meitei people). Under the shadow of a banyan tree, the elder chants:
‚ÄúDo we have to live like grass under their foot? 
Wake up, Yelhoumee, sons and daughters of the Salai Taret!‚Äù
Here, Salai Taret refers to the seven clan lineages (Salai) and "Taret" means seven in Meitei-lon.
This powerful moment bridges the past and present‚Äîa cry for unity and cultural survival.
‚ÄúWe Outside‚Äù is a song for those who have been silenced ‚Äî a voice for the displaced, the grieving, and the unbroken. It belongs on playlists that spotlight politically charged rap, regional resistance, raw lyricism, and the emerging fire of East Indian hip-hop.

A film by Hype 79
Director - Krishna Thokchom
Cinematography/Editor - Narry Takhellambam
Drone - Abung
VFX - Naocha

Cast - Augustine Shimray (Featherheads), Oja Sajoubi (Outro), Joy Khundrakpam, Rajkumari Nevia, Mangal Kshetrimayum

Child Artist - Sinthalemba Nongthombam Meitei

Audio Credits:
Produced by Seej
Mixed and mastered by Skar

Video credits
Crew - Malem Sanasam, Rajesh Khaidem, Abung Wairokpam, Ronaldson Takhellambam, Adanial Tokpam, David, Sanathoi Ngairangbam, Niketan Akoijam, Hijam Sanatomba, Totto Thokchom, Skar, Nganba Sanoujam, Chinglen Nongthomgbam, Martin kaidem, Bishal Laisram, Thoithoiba Thokchom, Alish Nongthongbam, Trilokchand Posungbam, Malemnganba Mangsatabam, Somorjit khangebam, Devjit Yumnam, Mahesh Phijam, Lakhan Ngangom, Robinson Wakabam, Amaraj Leiphoubam, Rajesh Pebam, Sunildro Nongthombam, Parihanba Posungbam, AT Heingang Unit 33, Kanglei Hoops, Jonarth Seram, Jupiter Ningombam, Bilson Ngairangbam, Dingku Heisnam, Benish Leishangthem, Newton Thoidingjam, Ronan Warepam, Nelson Sharma, Ngouren Ningombam, Langamba Leiphrakpam, Leishemba Leishangthem, Prince Achom, Tyson Ngangbam, Prithiviraj Sarangthem, Meerel, Richard Rajkumar, Allen (chaoba), Tangku, Darick, Lamboikhongnangkhong gi ema ebel meira paibi sing

snippet.description:
Jaby & Achara react to the pulse-pounding trailer for War 2‚Äîa high-octane, cinematic showdown that‚Äôs set to take the YRF Spy Universe to explosive new heights.

Returning as the enigmatic super-soldier Kabir, Hrithik Roshan (Fighter, War) faces off against a powerful new force‚ÄîN. T. Rama Rao Jr. (RRR, Janatha Garage)‚Äîin a battle where loyalties blur and the cost of war runs deeper than ever. Directed by Ayan Mukerji (BrahmƒÅstra, Wake Up Sid), this sequel raises the bar with breathtaking scale, emotionally charged conflict, and edge-of-your-seat action.

From globe-trotting espionage and gritty hand-to-hand combat to larger-than-life stunts and an electrifying score, the War 2 trailer delivers pure cinematic adrenaline. Vivian & Brandon break it all down‚Äîthe mind games, the mythic rivalries, and the epic visuals that hint at something far bigger than just a battle between two men.

This isn't just a fight. It's a reckoning. And if the trailer is anything to go by, War 2 is set to become a genre-defining spectacle.

‚Äî AVATAR 3: FIRE AND ASH

‚Äî This video is a fan-made concept trailer, created solely for artistic and entertainment purposes.The goal behind this trailer is to showcase my creativity and storytelling skills through a concept trailer based on a unique and original idea. By combining various effects, sound design, and AI technologies, I‚Äôve crafted a cinematic experience that reimagines familiar worlds in bold and imaginative ways. This trailer is not official and is intended to entertain, inspire, and engage with the YouTube community. Thank you for your support ‚Äî now let‚Äôs dive into a world shaped by creativity and craft. üé¨‚ú®

‚Äî  In this concept trailer for Avatar: Fire and Ash, Pandora reveals a darker side as old loyalties fracture and new fires take hold. Varang, leader of the Ash People, turns away from Eywa and leads a rising Na‚Äôvi clan that bends flame to its will, threatening not only balance but belief itself. Jake Sully, still bearing the weight of Neteyam‚Äôs loss, must hold his family together as they face not just the returning human forces, but a war born from within their own kind. Spider stands at a crossroads between the man who raised him and the father who now wears a Na‚Äôvi face, while Kiri, Lo‚Äôak, and Tuk each grapple with grief and transformation. With striking images of scorched cliffs, skyborne fleets, and firelit battlegrounds, the trailer paints a portrait of a story defined by legacy, fracture, and the unshaken bond of family: whatever comes, Sullys face it as one.

snippet.title: [URDU] 2025 PMWC at EWC Group Stage Day 1 | PUBG MOBILE WORLD CUP at ESPORTS WORLD CUP
snippet.description:
GROUP STAGE DAY 1 | JULY 25

2025 PUBG MOBILE WORLD CUP ka aghaaz ho chuka hai ESPORTS WORLD CUP ke sath, aik dhamakedar Group Stage k pehle din ke sath! Tayyar ho jao ek aur shaandaar summer ke liye jab duniya ki top PUBG MOBILE teams Riyadh mein takraayengi glory ,legacy , aur $3,000,000 ke inaam ke liye. Aao mil kar dekhein ke kaunsi teams HEAT ko BEAT kar paengi!

Yeh global showdown duniya bhar ki behtareen squads ko ikattha karta hai, jo sab 2025 PMWC jo k EWC ki taraf sy horha hai jeetne ka khwab le kar tayyar hain. Pehle ka aaghaz dhamakedaar matches ke saath hoga, jo agle teen dinon ki sakht muqabla baazi ka manzar zahir kryga.

Is safar ka aaghaz Group Stage se hoga, jahan 24 teams ko 3 groups mein taqseem kiya gya hai jo Grand Finals ke liye apni jagah banane ke liye takrayen gi. Is stage se top 8 teams seedha Grand Finals mein pohnchyn gi, jabke baaqi 16 teams high pressure Survival Stage mein aamna saamna karen gi aakhri 8 slots ke liye. Grand Finals mein 16 behtareen teams ek doosre ke khilaaf glory, pride, aur championship ka taaj pehnny k liye pury josh se takraengi.

üî• Ap 2025 PMWC jo k EWC mai horha hai miss nahe krna chahyngy.

- Dekho duniya ki top PUBG MOBILE teams ko Riyadh mein apne waqar ke liye takraate hue!
- Har match mein high-stakes action ka lutf uthao, jo har dafa is dorh ko badal kar rakh dega.
- Apne pasandeeda region aur teamon ko cheer karo jab woh $3,000,000 aur  ke taj k peche bhaag rahe hongy!
- Grand Finals mein hoga zabardast SMASH RULE format to tayyar ho jao excitement ke liye!

üî• SMASH RULE Grand Finals mein kaise kaam karta hai?

Grand Finals ke doosry din ke baad, Match Point Threshold set kiya jata hai jo ke #1 ranked team ke points mai 10 points jamah kr k banta hai. Jo bhi team is threshold ko cross karti hai, usay phir kisi baad wale match mein jeet hasil karni hoti hai taake woh trophy apne naam kar sake, jis match mein woh threshold cross karti hai, agar usi mein jeeti to bhi woh champion nahi banegi.

Agar Match 18 tak koi team SMASH Rule ke zariye title secure nahi karti, to standard rules ke mutabiq sabse zyada total points wali team ko winner declare kiya jata hai.

Survival Stage: July 29‚Äì30

From Warner Bros. Pictures and Academy Award-nominated, BAFTA-winning filmmaker Paul Thomas Anderson comes ‚ÄúOne Battle After Another,‚Äù starring Academy Award and BAFTA winner
Leonardo DiCaprio.

Oscar and BAFTA winners Sean Penn and Benicio del Toro also star alongside Regina Hall, Teyana Taylor and Chase Infiniti, as well as Wood Harris and Alana Haim.

Anderson directs from his own screenplay. The producers are Oscar and BAFTA nominees Adam Somner and Sara Murphy and Anderson, with Will Weiske executive producing.

The creative team behind the camera includes several frequent collaborators, among them directors of photography Michael Bauman and Anderson; Oscar-nominated, BAFTA-winning production designer Florencia Martin; BAFTA-nominated editor Andy Jurgensen; Oscar and BAFTA-winning costume designer Colleen Atwood; casting director Cassandra Kulukundis; and with music by Oscar- and BAFTA-nominated composer Jonny Greenwood.

snippet.description:
Ik Nal Gal Ni Bani - Manmohan Waris

Music: Sangtar
Lyrics: Kundha Singh Dhaliwal
Album: Punjabi Virsa 2024 PNE
Label: Plasma Records

Manmohan Waris, Kamal Heer & Sangtar's Punjabi Virsa 2024 PNE was recorded on August 31st, 2024 at Pacific Coliseum as part of the PNE Fair - Summer Nights Festival in Vancouver, Canada. 
Show Presenters: Jas Aujla, Binder Grewal, Satti Kang, Jassi Garcha & Pindy Thoor
Accompanying musicians: Subhash Kali (Tabla), Sukhwinder Bunty (Dholak), Rohit Anand (Keyboards), Sangtar (Linnstrument, Tumbi, Mandolin), Sukhwinder Ladi (Acoustic and Electronic Drums), BM Khan (Guitar), Akhtar Ali (Keyboards), Gaurav (Dhole) and Amar Heer (Keyboards).
Lyricists: Kundha Singh Dhaliwal, Mangal Hathur, Debi Makhsoospuri, Jasbir Gunachauria, Davinder Khannewala, Gill Ranuta, Sukhpal Aujla, Sukhwinder Amrit, Dhadi Amar Singh Shaunki, Sangtar.
Sound And Lights: Pindy Thoor, Thoor Electronics
